Prisoner was found guilty of manslaughter; 

she pleaded guilty of using an instrument to procure miscarriage in the cases of Goode and Collier; 

she was found Not guilty of murder.

Verdict, 

                     Reginald Treloar, Guilty; 

                     G. R. Treloar, Not guilty. The second indictment was not proceeded with.
